## A
1. pull the OS image
<code>docker pull ubuntu:latest</code>

2. list all installed containers
<code>docker container ls -all</code>
<code>docker container ls</code> for only running containers

3. install webserver
<code>docker run --detach --publish 80:80 --name webserver nginx</code>

4. stop running container
<code>docker container stop <i>containers_name</i></code>

## B

